videos.headline: UNLV QB fumbles snap, recovers and scores
videos.description: Armani Rogers fumbles the exchange and then recovers the to score a 1-yard TD for the first score of the game.

videos.headline: UNLV starts half with 60-yard TD run
videos.description: UNLV RB Lexington Thomas darts up the middle and is gone for 60 yards as the Rebels run ahead 17-3.

videos.headline: UNLV RB Thomas rumbles in from one yard out.
videos.description: RB Lexington Thomas scores his second TD of the day at the goal line for the Rebels.

videos.headline: UNLV RB Thomas scores third TD on 62-yard run
videos.description: RB Lexington Thomas extends the Rebels lead following his 62-yard TD dash in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Idaho QB avoids sack, creatively scores
videos.description: QB Matt Linehan rolls out to the right and lobs a TD to a wide open Reuben Mwehla.

videos.headline: Rogers connects with Boyd for 94-yard TD
videos.description: UNLV responds to Idaho State's TD with a lightning quick 94-yard score.
